data.description: Extremely spacious home featuring SOLAR PANELS, 5 beds/2.5 baths & the amazing amenities Rolling Hills neighborhood has to offer! Average electric bill just $30 a month! Located minutes from future toll rd extension! Downstairs you will find 1 of 5 bedrooms (or office), a half bath, a formal dining area, huge chef's kitchen w/ eat in space & informal dining opening up to a spacious living area. Ceramic tiles throughout! Upstairs you will find an amazing flex space, perfect for another living space or play area. There is a huge master suite w/ garden tub & sep shower, spacious his & hers closets. 3 further bedrooms, with a family bath. Laundry located on the upstairs. Amenities include resident's club, resort style pool & tennis courts!
